With widening optics Myrmidon watched as the would be opponant flew
inside the base, some how shooting past the other defenders. 

&quot;Fool!&quot; Myrmidon growled. Weather he was talking about the intruder or
the defenders at the door it is difficult to tell. 

With a thought Myrmidon shifted form assuming his avian mode and
followed. While he was smaller, about the size of a large eagle, he was
outfitted with boosters amd missile launchers. He fired the former as
he pursued Malice into the base as he primed the latter, ready for what
would come next. 

