sensors taking in the residual heat signature and exaust output. Even
for one without sensors Malice wasn&#39;t difficult to follow - the sounds
of internal defences attempting to capture or kill him was a finger
pointing directly at him. 

Arriving at the door just after Malice entered his hidey hole of a
room, Myrmidon smiled. &quot;Good, you have trapped yourself. There are no
other doors here.&quot; He nodded as he heard the bulkheads dropping down in
different part of the base. 

&quot;Computer!&quot; Myrmidon crossed his arms over his chest. &quot;Erect a maximum
strength forceshield around ante cabin 447 and deactivate power.&quot;

